    RetrieveData -->|datasets API| LlamaStackServer
    RunRagas -->|completions + embeddings| LlamaStackServer

    InlineLLM -->|inference API| LlamaStackServer
    InlineEmbed -->|embeddings API| LlamaStackServer

    LlamaStackServer -->|inference| Ollama[Ollama<br/>11434/TCP HTTP]
    LlamaStackServer -->|inference| VLLM[vLLM<br/>HTTPS configurable]

    RunRagas -->|results upload| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RemoteEval -->|results download| S3

    RemoteEval -->|read ConfigMap| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RemoteEval -->|base image ref| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator<br/>ConfigMap]

